Sentencas: Oxygen diffusion was measured at oxygen/cathode/electrolyte interfaces and at oxide scales/alloy interconnects in Solid Oxide Fuel Cells (SOFCs).
Titulo: Diffusion of oxygen at ceramic interfaces for high-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: A stable isotope oxygen exchange technique (O-16/O-18 exchange) was adopted to label the diffusion profiles in the oxides, and secondary ion mass spectrometry (SIMS) depth profiles were examined to determine the diffusion coefficients in the oxide ceramic materials.
Titulo: Diffusion of oxygen at ceramic interfaces for high-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Diffusivity of oxygen in LaMnO3 cathode was measured under polarized condition (that is, considering the electrochemical process and diffusion).
Titulo: Diffusion of oxygen at ceramic interfaces for high-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Also, oxygen diffusion in the oxide scales formed on the alloy was measured to clarify the formation mechanism of oxide scale.
Titulo: Diffusion of oxygen at ceramic interfaces for high-temperature solid oxide fuel cells
